Celeste Classic 2: Lani's Trek - GameTank port
==============================================

Original game "Celeste Classic 2: Lani's Trek" by ExOK Games, PICO-8.
  Design & code: Maddy Thorson and Noel Berry
  Music:         Lena Raine
  Sound effects: Kevin Regamey
  Released on the Lexaloffle BBS: https://www.lexaloffle.com/bbs/?tid=41282

The original cart is licensed by its authors under
Creative Commons Attribution-NonCommercial-ShareAlike 4.0 International
(CC BY-NC-SA 4.0).

This GameTank adaptation (the hand-translated game logic and physics in
main.lua, the map/data/sprite generator tooling in gen/gen.mjs, the banked
build driver in build.mjs, the re-encoded room data, and the mirrored sprite
cells) is a derivative work and is released by the same authorship terms under
the SAME license: CC BY-NC-SA 4.0.

Credit: original game, art, level design, music, and sound by ExOK Games
(Maddy Thorson, Noel Berry, Lena Raine, Kevin Regamey). GameTank port for the
gtlua SDK by Luis Montes.

